[SN]TITLE[SN]
F1's greatest livery - you tell us your favourite colour schemes

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
McLaren's new colour scheme, unveiled at this weekend's Spanish Grand Prix, has sparked a lively debate about the sport's greatest ever liveries.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Clearly a subjective issue like this could never hope to deliver a definitive answer - yet it is a debate in which F1 fans love to immerse themselves, time and time again.
Here at BBC Sport we are no different, and over on our Spanish GP practice live page we have been having a vote - from a shortlist based on readers' nominations on social media - to see which livery stands out from the crowd.
